  "firstAcquaintance": "A clown who performs at parties. Though she doesn't like to talk much, she puts everything into her performances.",
  "personality": "Introverted and always comes across as shy when speaking. She blushes easily and then hides away.",
  "like": "Masks, cute clothes",
  "familiarData": "Yuri's true identity is that of an assassin from a mysterious wanderer organization called the 'Recluses,' skilled at wearing various disguises to carry out espionage and assassination missions.\nShe is one of the organization's top operatives, possessing a unique technique of mental rehearsal that allows her to simulate the assassination process with remarkable accuracy. She is also adept at weaving magic into her kills, using unexpected methods to eliminate her targets.\nHowever, she has a personality weakness: if someone stares at her continuously, she gets embarrassed and wants to hide. It's somewhat manageable when she wears a mask, but without one, she often can't even bring herself to speak to people.\nWhile her shyness is an obvious weakness, don't ever think you can exploit it, especially when it comes to removing her mask. Absolutely not. Absolutely not. Absolutely not. It bears repeating three times because it is extremely dangerous.\nShe knows Ruyiling and is aware of Ruyiling's past, but she keeps secrets tight. Ask her about it and you'll only get the response: 'That is a restricted topic.'",
